<article class="env-theorem" id="00AA">
  <p><a class="environment-identifier" href="/tag/00AA">Theorem <span data-tag="00AA">14.9.1</span>.</a> There exists an $(\infty , n)$ category $\mathbf{Bord}_ n$ whose objects are points, …, $n$-morphisms are $n$-dimensional manifolds with corners. </p>
</article>